ğŸ•³ï¸ Pothole Detection System using OpenCV | For Municipal Corporation & Smart Vehicles

This repository contains a Python-based Pothole Detection System designed for deployment in municipal corporation vehicles, road inspection units, and smart transportation systems.

The system processes video frames in real-time, uses OpenCV for image operations, NumPy for matrix processing, and time module for performance measurement.
It can be integrated into government surveillance vehicles to automatically detect potholes on roads and generate alerts.

