âš™ï¸ How It Works
1. Frame Capture

The system captures video frames using:

cv2.VideoCapture(0) for live camera

Or a video file path

2. Preprocessing

Each frame is processed using:

Grayscale conversion

Gaussian blur

Edge detection (Canny)

Thresholding for dark pothole regions

ğŸ¯ Output Example

Potholes highlighted with rectangles

FPS displayed on the frame

Real-time detection


